@startuml
title Normalize Stage - State Machine Diagram (Current)
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #eaf8e6
  BorderColor #b7ddb0
}

[*] --> Input

Input --> UpstreamBlocked : collected.errors exists
Input --> Prepare : no upstream errors

Prepare --> NoRow : source.row is None
Prepare --> ApplyRules : source.row exists

ApplyRules --> SinkValidation
SinkValidation --> Failed : normalize/sink errors
SinkValidation --> Normalized : no errors

NoRow --> Output
Failed --> Output
Normalized --> Output
UpstreamBlocked --> Output
Output --> [*]

note right of SinkValidation
Unlike MAP, sink validation here is strict\n(check_types=True).
end note

@enduml
